data.description: ***PRICED TO SELL*** PLEASE SUBMIT FINAL & BEST OFFERS!! Close to all amenities. Beautiful Gated Community w/ Pool, Spa and RV parking. This charming single story home features 2 bed/2 bath and sits nestled in a quiet cul de sac in Villa Sedona. The home has an open floorplan w/ fireplace, breakfast bar, a patio, and a two-car garage. Upgraded features include title, hardwood floors and fresh interior paint throughout. All appliances included as well as washer and dryer.
